layers.nm: A journey of a thousand websites begins with a SINGLE  pixel... As an ardent web designer, I've beheld the magic and  magic is the uncanny transformation of a simple webpage  into a storybook with the magic wand known as "effective  UX/UI design.”  It's all about the design story...  A captivating homepage is the 'chapter one' that draws  you in. It's the story's summary with just enough intrigue  to pique interest. Your audience needs to know right away  what they can gain from your site.  Now, let's talk navigation - it is our 'contents page.' An  elusive one might create intrigue, but a crystal clear  navigation opens the door to explore the rest of your storybook without frustration.
